---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import CTASection from '../components/CTASection.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="About ForgeRPA"
  description="Practical finance automation built by people with deep operations experience. We help accounting and finance teams eliminate manual work and focus on higher-value activities."
  heroTitle="Operations Experience That Builds Better Automation"
  heroSubtitle="We’ve lived the challenges of finance and accounting. Now we automate them."
>
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <!-- Background -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6">Our Approach</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          ForgeRPA was founded on a simple observation: the people who understand business processes best are rarely the ones building the automations. That gap leads to solutions that look good in demos but fall apart in production.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          With over 30 years of hands-on experience in finance and operations, our team has closed the books, managed reconciliations, prepared financial reports, and lived the daily challenges that finance teams face. This practical experience shapes every automation we build.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          We combine deep knowledge of accounting processes with technical expertise in RPA, data automation, and system integration. The result is practical, maintainable automation that delivers real ROI — not just impressive demos.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Experience -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6">Experience</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-slate-light rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-3">📊</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Finance & Operations</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              30+ years working in accounting, financial reporting, reconciliations, and month-end close processes across multiple industries. We understand the real challenges finance teams face because we've lived them.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-light rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-3xl mb-3">🤖</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-charcoal mb-2">Automation Expertise</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">
              Certified in RPA development with extensive experience building practical automation solutions. We specialize in turning complex manual processes into reliable, maintainable systems.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Philosophy -->
      <div class="mb-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-charcoal to-charcoal-light rounded-xl p-8 lg:p-12">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber mb-4">Our Philosophy</h2>
        <blockquote class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed italic">
          "The best automations aren't built by pure technologists or pure accountants — they're built by people who deeply understand both the business process and how to automate it effectively."
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <!-- Industries -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-charcoal mb-6">Industries Served</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          {['Manufacturing', 'Financial Services', 'Insurance', 'Restaurant & Hospitality', 'Professional Services', 'Healthcare', 'Technology', 'Utilities'].map((industry) => (
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-amber/10 text-amber-dark font-medium rounded-lg text-sm">
              {industry}
            </span>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600 text-sm">These are a few of the industries we have worked in. Our approach applies to any organization with manual finance and accounting processes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTASection
    heading="Let's Talk About Your Processes"
    subtext="30 minutes. No sales pitch. Just an honest conversation about where automation can make the biggest impact for your team."
    ctaText="Book a Discovery Call"
    ctaLink="/contact"
  />
</PageLayout>
